T1215 Kernel Modules and Extensions

Persistence

Loadable Kernel Modules (or LKMs) are pieces of code that can be loaded and unloaded into the kernel upon demand. Learn more

References suspicious system modules

T1124 System Time Discovery

Discovery

The system time is set and stored by the Windows Time Service within a domain to maintain time synchronization between systems and services in an enterprise network. Learn more

Contains ability to query machine time
